  "title": "Unit 10: Indefinite Pronouns & Question Tags",
  "grammarTopics": ["Indefinite Pronouns", "Question Tags"],
  "theory": {
    "brief": "Indefinite pronouns (someone, anyone, no one, everyone, something, anything, nothing, everything, somewhere, anywhere, nowhere, everywhere) dùng để nói về người/vật/nơi không xác định. Question tags là câu hỏi đuôi để xác nhận thông tin.",
    "examples": [
      "Someone is at the door. (indefinite pronoun)",
      "There isn't anything in the box. (negative + anything)",
      "You're happy, aren't you? (question tag)"
    ]
  },
